text = "Basic Movement Demo

This scene demonstrates basic movement including:
 * Left Controller:
   - Joystick U/D/L/R: Smooth Movement with strafing
   - A/X Button: Jump
 * Right Controller:
   - Joystick U/D: Smooth Movement
   - Joystick L/R: Smooth Turning
   - A/X Button: Jump

Test objects have been placed in the scene to allow testing of the different movement mechanics. The ramps and slopes are useful for evaluating how movement settings affect how easily the player can navigate checked different terrain."

